message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you. Given its high value and potential impact on your endeavors, I am offering it to you at a special price of $13500. This represents an excellent opportunity for you to acquire a valuable asset at a rate that is significantly below its market value of $15000. Please let me know if you have any questions or if you wish to proceed with this exclusive offer. I look forward to your positive response.
